OL,3,CTV-related anniversaries for 12 JUN
OL,4,CCHANNELS
OL,5,
OL,6,CG1967FThe ITA announces the results of
OL,7,Fthe 1967 ITV franchise round, which
OL,8,Fsees a number of changes to the ITV
OL,9,Fregional map. The changes were to be
OL,10,Fimplemented between May and August
OL,11,F1968:
OL,12,
OL,13,F(a) Any split weekday/weekend licences
OL,14,Fare removed in all regions, except
OL,15,FLondon;
OL,16,
OL,17,F(b) The London split is moved to Friday
OL,18,Fat 7pm;
OL,19,
OL,20,F(c) The north of England region is
OL,21,Fsplit into the north west and
OL,22,FYorkshire;
OL,23,Sppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppp
OL,24,ANext PageBOn This DayCClean FeedFNat TV
