OL,2,W+.!/*% *%*%/*%,.! /.!/*%,.!S,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,CTV-related anniversaries for 12 JUN
OL,4,CCHANNELS
OL,5,
OL,6,CG1995FL!ve TV begins broadcasting. The
OL,7,Fcable-only channel is perhaps
OL,8,Fremembered for its low-brow content,
OL,9,Fsuch as Topless Darts, Tiffany's Big
OL,10,FCity Tips (where model Tiffany Banister
OL,11,Frelayed financial news while stripping
OL,12,Fto her underwear) and News Bunny (where
OL,13,Fa person in a rabbit suit stood behind
OL,14,Fa news presenter, reacting to each
OL,15,Fstory).
OL,16,
OL,17,FThe channel was operated by Mirror
OL,18,FGroup Newspapers. At launch, it was
OL,19,Fheaded by Kelvin MacKenzie, with Janet
OL,20,FStreet-Porter as managing director. It
OL,21,Ffeatured a host of young presenters who
OL,22,Fwere new to TV. Presenters included:
OL,23,Sppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppp
OL,24,ANext PageBOn This DayCClean FeedFNat TV
